---
description: Clean Architecture and Provider conventions for face_vision
alwaysApply: true
---

# Architecture

- Layers: `presentation -> domain <- data`. Domain is pure Dart only.
- No `package:flutter` or `opencv_dart` imports in `lib/domain/`.
- OpenCV/FFI only in `lib/data/datasources/`.
- `data` implements `domain` repository interfaces.

# State management

- Use `provider`: `ChangeNotifier` + `ChangeNotifierProvider`.
- Widgets: UI only. Flow: widget -> provider -> use case -> repository.
- No business logic in widgets or `build()`.

# Use cases and entities

- One responsibility per use case; expose `Future<T> call(...)`.
- Entities are immutable in `lib/domain/entities/`.
- Map raw OpenCV output to entities in the data layer, not in presentation.

# New code checklist

- Repository interface in domain, implementation in data.
- Register wiring in `main.dart` composition root only.
